e0 di teol. di Helsinki (1990), Montreal (2006) e Jena (2009)."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1678129", "itemLabel": "Jacques Waardenburg", "dhsid": "044650", "namefr": "Jean Jacques Waardenburg", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Jacques_Waardenburg", "namede": "Jean Jacques Waardenburg", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Jacques_Waardenburg", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "119476568"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1678129", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": null, "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/044650/2012-12-05"}